Currently, the IssueService report API has only a method to retrieve an issue using an issue key. It should also provide a method to retrieve the issue using the issue ID. I have developed a UI that stores relationships using ID since the issue key can change if the issue is moved. This provides a richer API.

For example:
public RemoteIssue getIssue(User user, Long issueId) throws RemoteException, RemotePermissionException;

